OL,3,CVaping tax expected to be announced by
OL,4,CChancellor as part of Spring Budget
OL,6,FThe government is expected to announce
OL,7,Fa tax on vaping in next week's Budget
OL,8,Fon March 6.
OL,10,FAccording to the Times, which first
OL,11,Freported the story, the tax is
OL,12,Fexpected to apply to the liquid in
OL,13,Fvapes, with higher levels of tax for
OL,14,Fproducts with more nicotine.
OL,16,FAlongside this the chancellor is also
OL,17,Fexpected to announce an increase in
OL,18,Ftobacco duty to keep vaping as a
OL,19,Fcheaper alternative to smoking.
